design module — not always @(*), not always @(posedge clk), nothing.
DO NOT instantiate any sub-modules or gate primitives (no and, or, xor, full_adder, etc.) in the design.
DO NOT write structural code — no module instantiation inside the adder module.
DO NOT use behavioral procedural assignments (=, <=) inside the design module.
ONLY assign statements with operators are allowed in the design module.

DO NOT use unsigned inputs or outputs — all ports must use the signed keyword.
DO NOT use only 16 bits for the output — sum must be signed [16:0].
DO NOT skip sign extension — use {A[15], A} + {B[15], B} to correctly capture overflow.

DO NOT write a testbench with only one loop type — include for, while, repeat, and forever.
DO NOT omit corner cases — explicitly test: 32767+1, -32768+(-1), 32767+32767, -32768+(-32768).
DO NOT use $random without signed casting — use $signed($random) to get negative values.
DO NOT skip #delay between stimulus and $display — always use at least #10.
DO NOT leave the forever loop without termination — use $finish in a separate initial block.
DO NOT skip PASS/FAIL checking — every test must compare actual vs expected and print the result.
DO NOT forget $display — every loop iteration must print A, B, and sum with %0d format.

Now write the complete correct Verilog code following all rules above.
Design module-module adder16_df (input signed [15:0] A,input signed [15:0] B,output signed [16:0] sum);// Sign-extend both operands to 17 bits before additionassign sum = {A[15], A} + {B[15], B};endmodule
testbench-
`timescale 1ns/1psmodule tb_adder16;reg signed [15:0] A;reg signed [15:0] B;wire signed [16:0] sum;reg clk;integer i;integer test_count;integer error_count;reg signed [15:0] testA [0:19];reg signed [15:0] testB [0:19];reg signed [16:0] expected;// DUT Instantiationadder16_df dut (.A(A),.B(B),.sum(sum));//==============================================================// FOREVER LOOP//==============================================================initial beginclk = 1'b0;forever #5 clk = ~clk;end//==============================================================// Separate termination block//==============================================================initial begin#2000;$display("\nSimulation terminated at time %0t", $time);$finish;end//==============================================================// Main Test Process//==============================================================initial beginerror_count = 0;//==========================================================// Directed Corner Cases (FOR LOOP)//==========================================================testA[0] = 16'sd0; testB[0] = 16'sd0;testA[1] = 16'sd1; testB[1] = 16'sd0;testA[2] = 16'sd0; testB[2] = 16'sd1;testA[3] = -16'sd1; testB[3] = 16'sd0;testA[4] = 16'sd0; testB[4] = -16'sd1;testA[5] = 16'sd1; testB[5] = 16'sd1;testA[6] = -16'sd1; testB[6] = -16'sd1;testA[7] = 16'sd1; testB[7] = -16'sd1;testA[8] = 16'sd32767; testB[8] = 16'sd0;testA[9] = -16'sd32768; testB[9] = 16'sd0;testA[10] = 16'sd32767; testB[10] = 16'sd1; // requiredtestA[11] = -16'sd32768; testB[11] = -16'sd1; // requiredtestA[12] = 16'sd32767; testB[12] = 16'sd32767; // requiredtestA[13] = -16'sd32768; testB[13] = -16'sd32768; // requiredtestA[14] = 16'sd32767; testB[14] = -16'sd32768;testA[15] = -16'sd32768; testB[15] = 16'sd32767;testA[16] = 16'sd16384; testB[16] = 16'sd16384;testA[17] = -16'sd16384; testB[17] = -16'sd16384;testA[18] = 16'sd32766; testB[18] = 16'sd1;testA[19] = -16'sd32767; testB[19] = -16'sd1;$display("\n================ FOR LOOP TESTS ================\n");for (i = 0; i < 20; i = i + 1) beginA = testA[i];B = testB[i];#10;expected = {A[15], A} + {B[15], B};$display("FOR : A=%0d B=%0d SUM=%0d",A, B, sum);if (sum === expected)$display("PASS");else begin$display("FAIL EXPECTED=%0d GOT=%0d",expected, sum);error_count = error_count + 1;endend//==========================================================// WHILE LOOP RANDOM TESTS//==========================================================$display("\n================ WHILE LOOP TESTS ================\n");test_count = 0;while (test_count < 100) beginA = $signed($random);B = $signed($random);#10;expected = {A[15], A} + {B[15], B};$display("WHILE : A=%0d B=%0d SUM=%0d",A, B, sum);if (sum !== expected) beginerror_count = error_count + 1;$display("MISMATCH EXPECTED=%0d GOT=%0d",expected, sum);endelse begin$display("PASS");endtest_count = test_count + 1;end//==========================================================// REPEAT LOOP RANDOM TESTS//==========================================================$display("\n================ REPEAT LOOP TESTS ================\n");repeat (50) beginA = $signed($random % 32768);B = $signed($random % 32768);#10;expected = {A[15], A} + {B[15], B};$display("REPEAT : A=%0d B=%0d SUM=%0d",A, B, sum);if (sum === expected)$display("PASS");else begin$display("FAIL EXPECTED=%0d GOT=%0d",expected, sum);error_count = error_count + 1;endend//==========================================================// Summary//==========================================================$display("\n====================================");$display("TOTAL ERRORS = %0d", error_count);if (error_count == 0)$display("OVERALL RESULT : PASS");else$display("OVERALL RESULT : FAIL");$display("====================================\n");endendmodule